## 6. Python 客户端接入示例

项目已提供封装好的客户端 `scripts/ai_huoke_integration_client.py`，可直接使用：

```python
from scripts.ai_huoke_integration_client import BrowserCollectorClient

client = BrowserCollectorClient(base_url="http://127.0.0.1:8005", timeout=240)

# 健康检查
print(client.health())

# 关键词采集
result = client.collect_content(
    keyword="贷款",
    max_items=10,
    need_detail=True,
    need_comments=True,
    dedup=True,
    timeout_sec=180,
)
print(f"采集到 {result['count']} 条内容")

# 单篇详情
detail = client.collect_detail(url="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/xxx")
print(detail)
```

### 其他语言接入

只需向 `http://<服务IP>:8005/api/collect/run` 发送 POST JSON 请求即可，无语言限制。

**cURL 示例：**
```bash
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8005/api/collect/run \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"platform":"xiaohongshu","keyword":"贷款","max_items":5}'
```

